---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import EyebrowHeading from '../components/EyebrowHeading.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Work — Baldwinson"
	description="Strategic engineering, systems resilience, and long-term operational clarity. Architecture, infrastructure strategy, and organizational design for mission-critical environments."
>
	<EyebrowHeading 
		title="Work"
		lead="Engagements focused on strategic engineering, systems resilience, and long-term operational clarity."
	/>

	<Section divider>
		<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
			At Baldwinson we partner with organizations at pivotal decision points, where infrastructure strategy, architecture evolution, or organizational scale must be reconciled with real-world constraints. This work is grounded in engineering discipline, contextual judgment, and a commitment to long-term continuity.
		</p>
	</Section>

	<Section divider>
		<div class="space-y-10">
			<div>
				<h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-medium text-foreground sm:text-lg">
					Engineering
				</h2>
				<p class="mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
					We provide architecture, design, and implementation of distributed systems with particular attention to correctness, maintainability, and operational clarity. Engineering decisions prioritize reduction of systemic risk and support resilient delivery across production environments.
				</p>
				<p class="mb-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 sm:text-base">Areas of specialization include:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
					<li>Cloud infrastructure and deployment strategy</li>
					<li>Cost optimization and efficiency in large-scale environments</li>
					<li>High-availability system design</li>
					<li>Observability, reliability, and performance optimization</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			
			<div>
				<h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-medium text-foreground sm:text-lg">
					Systems & Scale
				</h2>
				<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
					We design and operate mission-critical systems where infrastructure choices materially affect business continuity. This includes platform selection and evaluation, failure mode analysis, and scalability planning that anticipates future growth and adversarial conditions.
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<div>
				<h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-medium text-foreground sm:text-lg">
					Organizational Design
				</h2>
				<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
					We provide consultation on engineering team structure, ownership models, and decision frameworks. Work in this domain supports sustainable delivery, accountability boundaries, escalation paths, and cultural norms that align technical reality with business objectives.
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<div>
				<h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-medium text-foreground sm:text-lg">
					Advisory
				</h2>
				<p class="mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
					Strategic guidance on:
				</p>
				<ul class="mb-4 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
					<li>Technical direction and risk assessment</li>
					<li>Vendor and platform evaluation</li>
					<li>Build-versus-buy decisions</li>
					<li>Technical due diligence for infrastructure and architecture</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
					Advisory engagements emphasize evidence-based decision making and risk reduction over short-term expedients.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</Section>

	<Section>
		<p class="mb-6 site-eyebrow">
			When This Work Is Engaged
		</p>
		<p class="mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
			Engagement typically occurs at points of:
		</p>
		<ul class="mb-4 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
			<li>Architectural transition</li>
			<li>Organizational growth</li>
			<li>Platform or infrastructure reassessment</li>
			<li>Cost, resiliency, or continuity risk evaluation</li>
		</ul>
		<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
			Not all situations are a fit. For organizations exploring alignment or discussion related to this work, correspondence details are available on the <a href="/" class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-foreground/80">HQ page</a>.
		</p>
	</Section>
</Layout>
